name: Fufu's Foray
description:
The idea for this project was based off of the poem "Little Bunny Foo Foo".

Fufu's Foray was completed in 2018 using Adobe Illustrator, Photoshop, and Processing (p5.js). 

The music is "Itsy bitsy spider instrumental" by Green Orbs at Youtube music library

The font is "Baskerville Old Face"
